<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>ArkVault.ai – Coming Soon</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Your private, offline vault for AI conversations, notes, documents and knowledge. Migrate chats, preserve insights, access anywhere—no cloud, no leaks."/>
  <link rel="icon" href="data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22 viewBox=%220 0 100 100%22><text y=%22.9em%22 font-size=%2290%22>🗝️</text></svg>">
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0f0f1a;
      --text: #e0e0ff;
      --accent: #7c3aed;
      --accent-dark: #5b21b6;
      --card: #1a1a2e;
    }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 5.5rem);
      margin: 0.5rem 0;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #a78bfa, #7c3aed);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }
    .tagline {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      color: #c4b5fd;
      margin: 1rem 0 2rem;
      max-width: 700px;
    }
    .desc {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      max-width: 720px;
      opacity: 0.9;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }
    .features {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }
    .feature-card {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid #333366;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1.8rem;
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
    }
    .feature-card:hover {
      border-color: var(--accent);
      transform: translateY(-4px);
    }
    .feature-title {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      color: var(--accent);
      margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }
    form {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 1rem;
      max-width: 600px;
    }
    input {
      padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      border: 1px solid #444466;
      background: #1a1a2e;
      color: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 280px;
    }
    button {
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      background: var(--accent);
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }
    button:hover {
      background: var(--accent-dark);
    }
    footer {
      margin-top: 5rem;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      opacity: 0.7;
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      h1 { font-size: 3.5rem; }
      .tagline { font-size: 1.3rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <h1>ArkVault.ai</h1>
  <p class="tagline">Your Private, Offline Knowledge Vault</p>

  <p class="desc">
    Migrate AI conversations from any model. Store notes, documents, PDFs and insights securely on your device.  
    Query your entire knowledge base from any AI—without ever sending data to the cloud. No leaks. No lock-in.  
    Launching Q2 2026 — Veteran-built in Texas.
  </p>

  <div class="features">
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-title">100% Offline & Private</div>
      Everything runs on your machine. Your data never leaves your device.
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-title">Chat Migration</div>
      Export from ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Copilot — reload anywhere in open formats.
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-title">Permanent Knowledge Vault</div>
      Index PDFs, notes, journals. Search and query your own wisdom forever.
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-title">Insight Recall</div>
      Auto-surface patterns, summaries, forgotten details from your history.
    </div>
  </div>

  <form action="https://formspree.io/f/your-form-id" method="POST">
    <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Your email for early access" required aria-label="Email address"/>
    <button type="submit">Get Early Access</button>
  </form>

  <footer>
    Service-Disabled Veteran-Owned • Privacy First • Built in Texas
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
